        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">অনুচ্ছেদটি পড়ে </span><span class=\"english\">নিচের </span><span class=\"english\">প্রশ্নগুলোর উত্তর দাও:</span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\">২</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\"><span class=\"math\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>×</mo></math></span> </span><span class=\"english\"> ৫ = ১০</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">এমনি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সময়ে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হঠাৎ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একদিন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কানে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গেল</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">মৃত্যুঞ্জয়ের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সেই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাগানের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অংশীদার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">খুড়া</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তোলপাড়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করিয়া</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বেড়াইতেছেন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যে</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">গেল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গেল</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">গ্রামটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এবার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">রসাতলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গেল।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নালতের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মিত্তির</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বলিয়া</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সমাজে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তাঁর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মুখ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাহির</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করিবার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">রহিল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">না</span><span class=\"english\">-</span><span class=\"english\">অকালকুষ্মাণ্ডটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সাপুড়ের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মেয়ে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নিকা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করিয়া</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঘরে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আনিয়াছে।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শুধু</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নিকা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নয়</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তাও</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">না</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">চুলায়</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যাক</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তাহার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হাতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভাত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পর্যন্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">খাইতেছে।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গ্রামে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যদি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ইহার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শাসন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">না</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">থাকে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বনে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গিয়া</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বাস</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করিলেই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কোড়োলা</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">হরিপুরের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সমাজ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">একথা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">শুনিলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যে</span><span class=\"english\">-</span><span class=\"english\">ইত্যাদি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ইত্যাদি।</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">তখন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ছেলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বুড়ো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সকলের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">মুখেই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ওই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কথা</span><span class=\"english\">-</span><span class=\"english\">অ্যাঁ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">এ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হইল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কী</span><span class=\"english\">? </span><span class=\"english\">কলি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কি</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">সত্যই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">উল্টাইতে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বসিল।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(</span><span class=\"english\">ক</span><span class=\"english\">) </span><span class=\"english\">গ্রামটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">রসাতলে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">গেল</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বলা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হয়েছে কেন</span><span class=\"english\">?</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(</span><span class=\"english\">খ</span><span class=\"english\">)</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">“</span><span class=\"english\">কলি কি সত্যই উল্টাইতে বসিল</span><span class=\"english\">”—</span><span class=\"english\">এই উক্তিটির মাধ্যমে সমকালীন গ্রামীণ সমাজের কোন বিশ্বাস বা মনোভাবের প্রতিফলন ঘটেছে? </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(গ) </span><span class=\"english\">“</span><span class=\"english\">গ্রামে যদি ইহার শাসন না থাকে</span><span class=\"english\">”—</span><span class=\"english\">এখানে </span><span class=\"english\">‘</span><span class=\"english\">শাসন</span><span class=\"english\">’</span><span class=\"english\"> বলতে কী বোঝানো হয়েছে এবং কেন এই শাসনের প্রয়োজন অনুভূত হলো?</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(ঘ) </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দার্থ লেখ- </span><span class=\"english\">অকালকুষ্মাণ্ড</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">নিকা</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">কলি</span><span class=\"english\">, </span><span class=\"english\">তোলপাড়</span><span class=\"english\">। </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(ঙ) </span><span class=\"english\">‘</span><span class=\"english\">মৃত্যুঞ্জয়</span><span class=\"english\">’</span><span class=\"english\"> ও </span><span class=\"english\">‘</span><span class=\"english\">রসাতল</span><span class=\"english\">’</span><span class=\"english\"> শব্দের ব্যাসবাক্যসহ সমাস নির্ণয় করো।</span></p>",
