        "question_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">সপ্রসঙ্গ ব্যাখ্যা কর:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(ক) </span><span class=\"english\">“</span><span class=\"english\">তুমি অধম তাই বলিয়া আমি উত্তম হইব না কেন?</span><span class=\"english\">”</span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\">২.</span><span class=\"english\">৫</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">(খ) </span><span class=\"english\">“</span><span class=\"english\">সেই ফুল আমাদেরই প্রাণ।</span><span class=\"english\">”</span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><span class=\"english\">২.</span><span class=\"english\">৫</span></p>",
